                "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n               <jats:p>Sleipner is an 8% Cr-steel. Its property profile has been carefully balanced, producing a versatile tool steel that overcomes the limitations of the 12% Cr-steels. This datasheet provides information on composition, physical properties, and elasticity. It also includes information on high temperature performance and wear resistance as well as forming, heat treating, machining, and joining. Filing Code: TS-728. Producer or source: B\u00f6hler-Uddeholm North America.</jats:p>",
